# Site pages

## Standard frontmatter

Most pages open with:

```yaml
---
image:
  path: /images/Excelsior-logo.png
  type: image/png
  alt: Excelsior Fencing Club
description: "..."
site_name: Excelsior Fencing Club
title: "..."
---
```

## Coaches.md

- HTML tables with coach bio, `mailto:` links, and `/images/coaches/` photos
- **Active coaches** on site may differ from club VSC lists — verify `Coaches.md` before public copy
- Coaching alumni listed at bottom; do not add without approval

## Calendar.md

Pulls shared snippets via `{% include_relative News/... %}` (club times, holidays). Update included files rather than duplicating schedule text.

## Links.md

Curated external links; minimal edits unless adding vetted resources.

## Images

Place assets under `images/` (logo at `images/Excelsior-logo.png`). Use site-root paths in frontmatter (`/images/...`).

## Style

Site uses the **hacker** theme — keep markdown simple; inline HTML in `Coaches.md` is intentional. Preserve existing table/CSS patterns when editing.
